  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897170/extras/aa4f46c0606ba976d1f54575dd823ab8.webp?t=1762827268\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a martial artist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You trained desperately and challenge gyms after gyms </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to reach the peak of martial arts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Today, you're at a new gym waiting for you to take down─</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897170/extras/f64ea496406e7460fa0ac9747d045d79.webp?t=1762827268\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a fighting game controlled by clicking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left click to throw bodyshot and right click to throw jab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knock the opponent out to proceed to the next stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897170/extras/d7b4927e21616bdefab6af68db6104f6.webp?t=1762827268\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a real-time boxing game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the opponents down with your fists</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and experience the thrill of boxing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897170/extras/aa4f46c0606ba976d1f54575dd823ab8.webp?t=1762827268\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a martial artist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You trained desperately and challenge gyms after gyms </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >to reach the peak of martial arts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Today, you're at a new gym waiting for you to take down─</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897170/extras/f64ea496406e7460fa0ac9747d045d79.webp?t=1762827268\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a fighting game controlled by clicking.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left click to throw bodyshot and right click to throw jab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knock the opponent out to proceed to the next stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2897170/extras/d7b4927e21616bdefab6af68db6104f6.webp?t=1762827268\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a real-time boxing game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the opponents down with your fists</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and experience the thrill of boxing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
